<p>http://www.president.harvard.edu/speeches/2005/nber.html</p>

<p>Good article by Michael Lewis on the whole affair:</p>

<p>http://quote.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=10000039&amp;refer=columnist_lewis&amp;sid=aU8IJfLtmShA</p>

