<p class="posted">posted by Jason at March  6, 2005 01:18 PM <a href="001588#c4298">#</a></p>

</div><div id="c4301">

<p>gripdamage: the Rightists who are just &#8220;taken in by con-men&#8221; are often not supportive of Bush, or at least have some reservations about him. People who believe this Evil Leftist Academic Establishment sh!t are obviously too far down the path of stupidity. As someone else has put it, they weren&#8217;t reasoned into their positions, so they won&#8217;t be reasoned out of their positions either.</p>

